snippet.title: I GO UNDERCOVER as a HACKER to SAVE VY QWAINT
snippet.description:
VY GOT KIDNAPPED!

After Chad Wild Clay made "Come Back Daniel Song - Spy Ninjas (Official Music Video)", Vy Qwaint created "CHAD WILD CLAY's SECRET Reveal Could End the Spy Ninjas", Daniel Gizmo uploaded "OUR BEST FRIEND LOST HIS MIND in Hypnosis", and Melvin PZ9 filmed "We're Not Talking To Chad!" Vy is still upset at Chad for keeping a secret from their marriage. Even though Chad didn't know that donating a kidney would save the Project Zorgo Leader's life, Vy is so hurt that she takes off her wedding ring and asks for a break from the marriage. Heartbroken, Chad doesn't know what to do than ask for the Spy Ninjas advice. As Vy leaves the safehouse for good, she gets kidnapped by Horseradish and hackers! The Spy Ninjas receive a distress call from Vy and now they must rescue her! Chad wants to save his marriage and will do anything, even go undercover as a hacker! Daniel wants to put the Spy Ninjas back together, Melvin and Regina haven't fully forgiven Chad and his secret yet. As they go undercover, can Chad and Daniel fool the hackers all around the warehouse? Can Melvin and Regina help save Vy before anything bad happens? Are the Spy Ninjas back together after all this? Thank you for watching my funny entertainment comedy adventure vlog videos in 2021!
